data.description: This roomy Rogers home is the perfect blend of comfort and convenience with an inviting living area, ample cabinet space, and cozy dining nook with backyard views. The star of the show is the spacious backyard with room for all your outdoor activities, gardening projects, or simply relaxing on the covered patio. It's the perfect spot for barbecues, evening gatherings, or even your own private garden retreat. A key perk of the home is its proximity to downtown Rogers. You'll be just minutes away from a vibrant hub of restaurants, boutiques, and entertainment options. Whether you're enjoying a night out on the town or taking a leisurely stroll through the farmers' market, downtown Rogers offers an array of experiences for everyone. Don't miss the chance to make this beautiful Rogers home your own. With its roomy backyard, prime location, and spacious interior, it's the perfect place to create lasting memories.
